text: Kalidiatou Niakaté (born 15 March 1995) is a French handball player for Brest Bretagne Handball and the French national team.2017 World Women's Handball Championship roster2018 European Women's Handball Championship roster Her team placed second at the 2012/13 Cup Winners' Cup and 2013/14 Challenge Cup.Kalidiatou Niakaté. eurohandball.com ==References== Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:French female handball players Category:Sportspeople from Aubervilliers Category:European champions for France
